# Cloudflare API token for the certbot dns-cloudflare plugin.
#
# 1. Go to https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens
# 2. Create a token with permission: Zone -> DNS -> Edit, scoped to the
#    eazevedo.online zone only.
# 3. Copy this file to "cloudflare.ini" (same folder) and paste the token below.
# 4. chmod 600 cloudflare.ini  (certbot will refuse to run otherwise)
#
# NEVER commit the real cloudflare.ini file to git.

dns_cloudflare_api_token = your_cloudflare_api_token_here
